4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to the City of Jemison; to further provide for
10 the sale of draft beer in the city.
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
12 Section 1. The Jemison City Council, by resolution, may
13 authorize the sale or distribution of draft beer by retail
14 licensees of the Alcoholic Beverage Control Board in the City
15 of Jemison. The authorization shall include the sale of draft
16 beer for off-premises consumption in a growler, keg, or other
17 similar container by persons licensed by the board to make
18 retail sales for off-premises consumption.
19 Section 2. This act shall become effective immediately.
